Nonprofit Cloud for Grantmaking
Use Nonprofit Cloud for Grantmaking to create robust grant applications. Grant seekers can save progress and see incomplete sections. Collaborators can be added to complete sections in Experience Cloud.

Measure the Impact and Success of Grants with Outcome Management
Indicate funding opportunities and awards that drive outcomes. Create visibility into overall strategy and alignment across organizations.

Securely Collaborate on Grantmaking Application Sections
Add collaborators to help complete grant application sections in Experience Cloud.

Easily Add Grantmaking Permission Sets to Permission Set Groups
Add Grantmaking permission sets to permission set groups alongside custom permission sets.

Quickly Delete Individual Applications
Delete individual applications instead of setting them to inactive status.

New and Changed Objects for Grantmaking
Use new and updated Grantmaking and Outcome Management objects and fields.
